##CPGE_SCRIPT
##ScriptVersion: 1.0
##Written: 2026-05-10
##Scene: SCENE_GAMEOVER
##Author: LordAries1972
##Description: Game Over screen — halt all player systems, fade out, present game over.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Halt all running subsystems gracefully
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
STOP EFFECTS
STOP MUSIC
STOP MOUSE
STOP GAMEPAD

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Fade the screen to black over 1.5 seconds
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute FadeToBlack(1.5, 0.0)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Stop all player timers
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute StopPlayerTimer(0)
Execute SetPlayerState(0, 2)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Display game over alert, then wait for scene system to take over
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ALERT General "Game Over."

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Reset all player stats ready for a potential restart
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute ResetAllPlayerStats()
